reviews.review_text: - The only AUD available so far, and sadly unequalizable.
get real you actually listed them fucking around in between songs as an actual set list song?

Funiculi Funicula jonnyb73, if you're referring to the 4th tune in the list, Funiculi Funicula, hell yes it's a set piece! They pulled it out quite a few times over the years to give to the audience while they were tuning or whatever. But whenever they pulled it out, it's ALWAYS listed as a setlist song. History, man. :-)
